DarkNet Design Haus

We're a small group of passionate designers & developers each with our own area of expertise, working together with a common purpose.

We want to focus our skills & passion on the darknet, to provide your business the opportunity to grow, develop & display your brand, your way.

Branding & Logo Design

  • Our team crafts your visual and verbal brand.
  • Logo Design, Identity, Marketing Materials.
  • Image/Content Management (watermarking, image optimisation & editing).

Web Development & Security

  • Streamline code review process. No JS if needed.
  • We're across the latest vulnerabilities &
    attack strategies.
  • Multi-stage testing, review & support.

Ongoing Support

  • We're available at various hours to ensure we are contactable when needed.
  • We can be contacted via: BitMessage, Tox, Ricochet, Jabber, Bleep, Wickr, Telegram.

Goals & Relationships

  • We're seeking for long-term clients for whom we can be a dependable & seasoned partner.

Our Work

Well, kind of...

Whilst we cannot upload a full portfolio of our work for privacy reasons, we have designed a little overview of fictitious companies to help showcase a glimpse of what we can do. Further design examples can be provided upon request. Note: we do not disclose any clientele we work for, past or present.

Get In Touch

Service & Security

We are contactable via email only, until we determine that we are able to facilitate your needs. After-which we are more than happy to provide our other methods of contact.

To get started please send us an email outlining an overview of your requirements along with your preferred hours of contact and we'll get back to you within 48 hours with our proposal.
